Standards-Version: 1.0

Package: rm-trash
Architecture: all
Priority: optional
Description: Send deleted files safely into trash for later retrieval.
 "rm-trash" utility puts the files you delete in a shell safely into the Trash (Recycle bin).
 rm-trash solves accidental removals and unlike other such utilities
 it can handle duplicate files in the trash
 works for recursive arguments and any other options that rm supports
